reviews.review_text:
Another perfect CM transfer Thanks Charlie!
Peace, Bob
The Promised Land ending  is silly
Best Desolation Row Ever Set the time machine back to 1992..outside in Sunny California...Jerry just went off on Bertha and the Desolation..Best ever ! Can alomst hear the sunshine...

Box of Rain Firstly-- thanks to Charlie Miller. This is a much better recording than the first SB I heard...

Secondly-- this Cal Expo show was by no means perfect, but I knew that didn't happen. Trucking', for instance, is sloppy and loses momentum. 

Most of the show was, let me say, average for the Dead in 1992-- in other words wonderful to me! I do love 1992 Dead. 

Lastly-- I highly recommend the Box of Rain. Box, it turns out, is one of the sweetest Box I've heard...yeah-- in 1992! Go figure.
